l]</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"咁幾多個人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"當天,IU在下午2點舉行的第1部和6點舉行的第二部分別邀請了&quot;10多歲&quot;粉絲和20歲以上的粉絲,與出道後更加廣泛的各年齡層的uaena一起慶祝了特別的紀念日。並且<span style=\"color: red;\">IU當天向所有入場者贈送特別制作的粉絲俱樂部&quot;uaena&quot;情侶戒指和ASMR視頻CD,襪子,小卡等的&quot;IU Plus&quot;套裝,贈送了10周年禮物，給予了難忘的回憶。</span><br />\n<br />\n會場, 1082個位<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.uac.co.kr/2010_customer/seat_info.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uac.co.kr%2F2010_customer%2Fseat_info.asp&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d9d94ffb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uac.co.kr/2010_customer/seat_info.asp</a><br />\n韓場一定爆, 分上下兩場, 共2164份<br />\n參考taobao, 大約4.5g一只, 4.5*2164=9738g<br />\n3689.22hkd/kg *9.738=35925.62436hkd<br />\n當個加工貴一倍都係70000幾姐, 娘娘開口唱一首都唔只呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金佢都比得起, 同期佢都捐左70萬出去, 其實都係零用$黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://popbee.com/celebrities/celebrities-news/iu-korean-singer-10-anniversary-concert/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpopbee.com%2Fcelebrities%2Fcelebrities-news%2Fiu-korean-singer-10-anniversary-concert%2F&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=be43809d\" target=\"_blank\">https://popbee.com/celebrities/celebrities-news/iu-korean-singer-10-anniversary-concert/</a>"}]}